Problem Statement Selected

Intelligent Slack Knowledge Base
Project Description
Our project is an AI-powered Slack Knowledge Base Assistant. It helps employees upload documents, ask questions, summarize content, and retrieve company knowledge directly inside Slack.
It is built for employees, teams, managers, and new joiners who need quick access to company information. It solves the problem of scattered knowledge across documents, Slack threads, URLs, and files. The assistant helps users save time by giving clear, cited answers without needing to search manually or interrupt teammates.

